{"tid":427871,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"同過名校妹同普通band1妹拍拖 其實幾大分別","createTime":"2017-10-07T16:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T10:31:09.000Z","uid":54581,"like":31,"dislike":351,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a195a3980795b476593b8a70a5cf290953f1d6","tid":427871,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"小弟拍過幾次拖 名校妹同BAND 1妹都試過<br />\n<br />\n相處落最大分別我覺得係個性格<br />\n<br />\nMCS MSS SHCC SPCC...<br />\n只係同過依4間名校妹拍過拖<br />\n<br />\n佢地好少話想等男人養，好有個人主見，會揸緊每一秒去做有意義既野，不論係溫書，興趣，義工，實習etc.<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係真係十項全能，語文掂，音樂掂，畫畫掂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而普通既band1妹，我會話無乜主見/唔知自己想要啲咩，問佢想讀咩major/大學畢業有咩去向又講唔出<br />\n<br />\n有時住hall, 見佢可以煲劇就一日 叫佢地玩下case comp,參加下啲活動又唔肯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（利申 我都會hea, 但接受唔到一日唔做正經野）"},{"pid":"ba986e8a2a219e7302eff8c07c45bf21fefd04b1","tid":427871,"uid":40648,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"結論係？"},{"pid":"4b92c19be1a029b56935d1d9b52732462ba7aefd","tid":427871,"uid":54581,"like":3,"dislike":68,"score":-65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結論係？</blockquote><br />\n標題"},{"pid":"69269d3772cd903cf83c90f543173174a8ccb994","tid":427871,"uid":130732,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"同過band 1尾全級第一既女拍拖<br />\n平時冇乜主見 <br />\n但一到考試就痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自修室朝十晚十走唔甩<br />\n識搵錢 有生意頭腦 衰在脾氣差<br />\n不過都算好女黎 <br />\n但冇考試就同樓主所講一樣乜都唔願做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999ee9a76ee260066833024812136a228bcfc80a","tid":427871,"uid":38456,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"床上呢"},{"pid":"b3cee416654bd4f1f3c594c34aa59545846519e9","tid":427871,"uid":52911,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTim